      :Access Public Shared
      ‚ćĚ * 8.0.0 ‚čĄ 2026-06-23
      ‚ćĚ   * Packages updated. Newer MarkAPL means that "<>" in comments are now treated as HTML tags;
      ‚ćĚ     That means they are NOT translated to &lt; and &gt; anymore!
      ‚ćĚ   * Documentation polished/corrected.
      ‚ćĚ   * Bug fixes
      ‚ćĚ     `Reset` wrongly attempted to call `Init` rather than `Init_HTML`.
      ‚ćĚ * 7.1.4 ‚čĄ 2025-03-09
      ‚ćĚ   * Recognizing an ADOC instance when running improved for 20.0
      ‚ćĚ * 7.1.3 ‚čĄ 2025-01-27
      ‚ćĚ   * Bug fixes
      ‚ćĚ     * Problem with ]ADOC -??? fixed: overcome missing user command framework variable ##.SourceFile
      ‚ćĚ     * A `Version` function that returned a number rather than text crashed ADOC
      ‚ćĚ     * The absence of Tatin now results in a proper message (ADOC depends on Tatin)
      ‚ćĚ     * The date of version 7.1.2 was wrong (2023 instead of the correct 2024)
      ‚ćĚ     * Version dates added to the `History`
      ‚ćĚ * 7.1.2 ‚čĄ 2024-10-12
      ‚ćĚ   * Bug fixes:
      ‚ćĚ     * In case there is a `Public` function and it returns an empty vector, nothing should be
      ‚ćĚ       listed as public, but that was not the case.
      ‚ćĚ     * ADOC_Doc is not case sensitive anymore: adoc_doc and ADOC_DOC are found as well
      ‚ćĚ * 7.1.1 ‚čĄ 2024-10-11
      ‚ćĚ   * The user command now complains with a useful message when no argument is provided.
      ‚ćĚ     So far a DOMAIN ERROR was thrown.
      ‚ćĚ   * Safety net added (:Trap 0) when a `Public` function is executed
      ‚ćĚ   * Documentation on Tatin packages corrected
      ‚ćĚ * 7.1.0 ‚čĄ 2023-06-11
      ‚ćĚ   `]ADOC` will now process references pointing to a loaded Tatin package in a smart way
      ‚ćĚ * 7.0.1 ‚čĄ 2023-04-20
      ‚ćĚ   * Bug fix: under certain circumstances `Copyright` and/or `Version` and/or `History` did
      ‚ćĚ     not get a caption assigned
      ‚ćĚ * 7.0.0 ‚čĄ 2023-03-23
      ‚ćĚ   * Breaking change: requires 18.0 or better
      ‚ćĚ   * Breaking change: ADOC is now a Tatin package, and depends on Tatin packages
      ‚ćĚ   * Breaking change: "IncludeCss" removed from the default parameter space (CreateBrowseDefaults)
      ‚ćĚ   * Called without an argument ]ADoc now investigates the namespace it was called from
      ‚ćĚ   * New parameter `htmlFilename` added to the parameter space.
      ‚ćĚ   * `ADOC_Doc` may not be a function anymore: it **must** be a variable (vector of char vectors)
      ‚ćĚ   * Needs `APLTreeUtils2` but does not :Include `APLTreeUtils` anymore
      ‚ćĚ   * The reserved names `History`, `Version` and `Copyrigth` may (still) be functions, but they
      ‚ćĚ     can now also be variables
      ‚ćĚ   * The deprecated function `List` was removed
      ‚ćĚ   * Bug fixes
      ‚ćĚ     * In case ADOC_Doc did not carry any header...
      ‚ćĚ       * no TOC was injected into the HTML
      ‚ćĚ       * any `Version` function was ignored
      ‚ćĚ     * Sort sequence was wrong (`Hello` should be listed *before* `Hello1`)
      ‚ćĚ\\
      ‚ćĚ For information regarding older versions see <https://github.com/aplteam/ADOC/releases>
