    :Property  BrowserPath
    ‚ćĚ By definition any HTML file is displayed with the default browser.\\
    ‚ćĚ If you want to display an HTML page with a different browser you must provide the
    ‚ćĚ full path name including the name of the EXE.\\
    ‚ćĚ This property replaced `BrowserName` which was finally removed in 6.7.0.
