    :Section SpecialFunctions

    ‚ćĚ Any of the following three properties might cause a VALUE ERROR when called in a certain context.
    ‚ćĚ It happens when `Initial_HTML` was not executed and the property is therefore not available.
    ‚ćĚ We do not really need anything here but those 3 properties, so we make them default to 0.
    ‚ćĚ That's a bit messy, yes, but far easier than any "correct" approach. If this starts to hurt
    ‚ćĚ we need to call `Initial_HTML` instead, and clean up the mess, but I doubt that will ever happen.

    :Property ignoreCopyright
    :Access Public Shared
    ‚ćĚ Defaults to 1: If there is a niladic function `Copyright` (public shared) the result is processed,
    ‚ćĚ otherwise ignore that function, if there is any.
        ‚ąá r‚Üźget
          :If 2=‚éēNC'_ignoreCopyright'
              r‚Üź_ignoreCopyright
          :Else
              r‚Üź0
          :EndIf
        ‚ąá
        ‚ąá set arg
          (‚ąÜEM‚Üź'"ignoreCopyright" Must be a Boolean')‚éēSIGNAL 11/‚ć®~arg.NewValue‚ąä0 1
          _ignoreCopyright‚Üźarg.NewValue
        ‚ąá
    :EndProperty

    :Property ignoreHistory
    :Access Public Shared
    ‚ćĚ Defaults to 1: If there is a niladic function `History` (public shared) the result is processed,
    ‚ćĚ otherwise ignore that function, if there is any.
        ‚ąá r‚Üźget
          :If 2=‚éēNC'_ignoreHistory'
              r‚Üź_ignoreHistory
          :Else
              r‚Üź0
          :EndIf
        ‚ąá
        ‚ąá set arg
          (‚ąÜEM‚Üź'"ignoreHistory" must be a Boolean')‚éēSIGNAL 11/‚ć®~arg.NewValue‚ąä0 1
          _ignoreHistory‚Üźarg.NewValue
        ‚ąá
    :EndProperty

    :Property ignoreVersion
    :Access Public Shared
    ‚ćĚ Defaults to 1: If there is a niladic function `Version` (public shared), the result is processed,
    ‚ćĚ otherwise ignore that function, if there is any.
        ‚ąá r‚Üźget
          :If 2=‚éēNC'_ignoreVersion'
              r‚Üź_ignoreVersion
          :Else
              r‚Üź0
          :EndIf
        ‚ąá
        ‚ąá set arg
          (‚ąÜEM‚Üź'"ignoreVersion" must be a Boolean')‚éēSIGNAL 11/‚ć®~arg.NewValue‚ąä0 1
          _ignoreVersion‚Üźarg.NewValue
        ‚ąá
    :EndProperty

    :EndSection

    :Property view
    :Access Public Shared
    ‚ćĚ Defaults to 1: show the result in a (default) browser.
    ‚ćĚ If set to 0 that is suppressed. Useful for test cases.
