    ‚ąá CreateTopOfBody dummy;html;containers;k;l;chapterNo
    ‚ćĚ Creates the main toc with links to all chapters and adds
    ‚ćĚ also the main header to the top of the document.
      :Access Public Instance
      html‚Üź''
      :If 1<‚ČĘ_DOCS  ‚ćĚ Then we have a main TOC (several namespaces)
          :If ‚ą®/containers‚Üź'Container'‚ąė‚Č°¬®2‚äÉ¬®_META
              k‚Üźl‚Üź1
              html,‚Üź(('h1 ',((0=‚ČĘ_Title)/'id="topmost"'))tag'Table of Contents'),nl
              :For chapterNo :In ‚ć≥‚ČĘcontainers
                  :If chapterNo‚äÉcontainers
                      html,‚Üź'div'tag(‚ćēl),' ',('a href="#',GetChapterNo,'"')tag chapterNo‚äÉ_DOCS
                      l‚Üźl+1
                      k‚Üź1
                  :Else
                      html,‚Üź'div class="subtoc"'tag(‚ćēl-1),'.',(‚ćēk),'. ',('a href="#',GetChapterNo,'"')tag chapterNo‚äÉ_DOCS
                      k‚Üźk+1
                  :EndIf
              :EndFor
              html,‚Üź'div'tag'&nbsp;'
          :Else
              :If 0=‚ČĘ_SubTitles
                  html,‚Üź'<br />','ol id="toc"'tag‚äÉ,/'li'‚ąėtag¬®_DOCS{('a href="#',‚ćĶ,'"')tag ‚ćļ}¬®'ch'‚ąė,¬®¬Į4‚ÜĎ¬®'0000'‚ąė,¬®‚ćē¬®‚ć≥‚ČĘ_DOCS
              :Else
                  html,‚Üź{'<br />','ol id="toc"'tag‚äÉ,/'li'‚ąėtag¬®‚ćĶ{('a href="#',‚ćĶ,'"')tag ‚ćļ}¬®'ch'‚ąė,¬®¬Į4‚ÜĎ¬®'0000'‚ąė,¬®‚ćē¬®‚ć≥‚ČĘ‚ćĶ}','(‚Č†‚äÜ‚äĘ)_SubTitles
              :EndIf
          :EndIf
          html‚Üź'div id="maintoc"'tag html
      :EndIf
      :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘ_Title
          html‚Üź('h1 id="topmost"'tag _Title),nl,html
      :EndIf
      html‚Üź('<a id="verytop"></a>'),nl,html
      _HTML‚Üźhtml,_HTML
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá CreateDocFooter dummy;html
    ‚ćĚ Creates the footer of the document. Default for "Creator"
