    ‚ąá r‚ÜźShowDocumentation type;filename;path;cfg
    ‚ćĚ * type=1 shows the same information as ]ADOC -??? (read: ADOC adocs itself)
    ‚ćĚ * type=2 shows the "Advanced" document
      :Access Public Shared
