    ‚ąá FinaliseHtml dummy;head;html;path;screenStyles;printStyles;addExt;tmp;fn
    ‚ćĚ Finalise the HTML by adding header, title and meta tags.
    ‚ćĚ
    ‚ćĚ It also changes any http:// as well as mailto:// and file:// references
    ‚ćĚ into HTML anchors. After having called this method, the HTML is ready for being saved
    ‚ćĚ on disk. The property flag `htmlFinalised` is therefore set to 1.
