    ‚ąá vs‚Üźvs LoopOverPublicStuff chapterNo;thisStuff;thisType
      :For thisStuff :In vs.publicStuff
          {‚ćĶ:.}1‚Č†‚Č°vs.Body                                                       ‚ćĚ Internal test case - don't remove!
          thisType‚ÜźGetSingle thisStuff
          :Select thisType
          :Case 'Include'
              vs‚ÜźCreateHTML_ForInclude vs
          :Case 'Constructor'
              vs‚Üźvs CreateHTML_ForConstructor thisStuff chapterNo
          :Case 'Destructor'
              vs‚Üźvs CreateHTML_ForDestructor thisStuff
          :Case 'Property'
              vs‚Üźvs CreateHTML_ForProperty thisStuff chapterNo
          :Case 'Field'
              vs‚Üźvs CreateHTML_ForField thisStuff chapterNo
          :Case 'Variable'
