          :Case 'Operator'
              vs‚Üźvs CreateHTML_ForOperator thisStuff chapterNo
          :Case 'Interface Method'                                                ‚ćĚ implemented ones!
              vs‚Üźvs CreateHTML_ForInterFace data
          :EndSelect
      :EndFor
