    ‚ąá r‚Üź{methodType}PrepareSubLinks(data type scriptName);bool;noOf;links;list;list2;buff
      ‚ćĚ Prepare a link list for a given type.
      ‚ćĚ Make it a numbered list if there are more than 4 items.
      r‚Üź‚ć¨
      :If {6::1 ‚čĄ 1‚ä£OutputType}‚ć¨ ‚ćĚ is it an instance? (‚éēNC results differ in 20.0 from earlier versions)
      :OrIf OutputType‚Č°'Web'
          :If (‚äātype)‚ąä'Field' 'Function' 'Operator' 'Variable'
              noOf‚Üź+/bool‚Üźtype‚ąė‚Č°¬®Get data
          :ElseIf 'Property'‚Č°type
              bool‚Üźtype‚ąė‚Č°¬®Get data
              noOf‚Üź‚ČĘ‚ÜĎ,/{','‚ąä‚ćĶ:','P.APLTreeUtils2.Split ‚ćĶ ‚čĄ ‚äā‚ćĶ}¬®'name'Get bool/data
          :ElseIf 'Interface Method'‚Č°type
              noOf‚Üź+/bool‚Üź('Interface Method'‚ąė‚Č°¬®Get data)
          :ElseIf 'Operators'‚Č°type
              noOf‚Üź+/bool‚Üź('Operator'‚ąė‚Č°¬®Get data)
          :Else
              noOf‚Üź+/bool‚Üź((Get data)‚ąä'Method' 'Function')‚ąßmethodType‚ąė‚Č°¬®'access'Get data
          :EndIf
          :If 0<+/bool
              :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘlist‚Üź'name'Get bool/data
              :AndIf 0‚Č†‚ČĘlist‚Üź(0<‚ČĘ¬®list)/list
                  list2‚Üź,‚ÜĎ,/{','‚ąä‚ćĶ:','P.APLTreeUtils2.Split ‚ćĶ ‚čĄ ‚äā‚ćĶ}¬®list
                  list2‚Üź{‚ćĶ‚ÜĎ‚ć®¬Į1+‚ćĶ‚ć≥'‚Üź'}¬®list2
                  list2‚Üźlist2[SortAlphabet‚ćč‚äÉlist2]
                  list‚Üźlist[SortAlphabet‚ćč‚äÉlist]
                  :If 1<‚ČĘlist2
                      :If 4‚Č•‚ČĘlist2
                          links‚Üźnl,‚ć®‚äÉ,/{‚ćļ,' | ',‚ćĶ}/{('a href="#',(GetChapterNo,':',‚ćĶ),'"')tag ‚ćĶ}¬®list2
                          r‚Üź'div class="sublinks"'tag links
                      :Else
                          buff‚Üź‚ÜĎ,/{(1+','+.=‚ćĶ)‚ćī‚äā‚ćĶ}¬®list
                          buff‚Üź',_'‚ąėReplace¬®buff
                          links‚Üź'ol class="sublinks"'tag‚äÉ,/'li'‚ąėtag¬®list2{('a href="#',(GetChapterNo,':',‚ćĶ),'"')tag ‚ćļ}¬®buff
                          r‚Üź'div class="sublinks"'tag links
                      :EndIf
                  :EndIf
              :EndIf
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚Üźtype SortMethods data;bool;buffer
      ‚ćĚ Sort the methods in "data" alphabetically. "type" is one of: Instance, Shared or Public (Interface!)
      :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘr‚Üźdata
