      :AndIf ~(‚äāname)‚ąävs.public
          :Return
      :EndIf
      syntax‚ÜźGetSyntax 1‚äÉvs.origSource
      (masked source)‚ÜźnoOf‚ÜĎ¬®vs.(maskedSource origSource)
      :If 0<+/bool‚Üź‚ą®/¬®‚ą®/¬®':implements constructor' ':implements destructor' ':implements method '‚ć∑¬®‚äābuffer
          :Select ‚ÜĎbool‚ć≥1
          :Case 1
              type‚Üź'Constructor'
              access‚Üź'Public'
          :Case 2
              type‚Üź'Destructor'
              access‚Üź'Private'
          :Case 3 ‚ćĚ interface method
              type‚Üź'Interface Method'
              access‚Üź'Public'
              more,‚Üź‚äā1‚Üď‚ÜĎ(‚ą®/':implements '‚ć∑‚äÉmasked)/source
          :EndSelect
      :Else
          :If vs.isNamespace
              access‚Üź'Shared'
              type‚Üź(1+3.1=scriptRef.‚éēNC‚äāname)‚äÉ'Operator' 'Function'
              :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘvs.public
              :AndIf ~(‚äāname)‚ąävs.public
                  :Return
              :EndIf
              buffer‚Üź''
          :ElseIf ‚ą®/‚ą®/':access'‚ć∑buffer
              type‚Üź'Method'
              buffer‚Ć∑[1]‚ć®‚Üź1‚ć≥‚ć®‚ą®/':access '‚ć∑buffer
              :If ‚ą®/'shared'‚ć∑buffer
                  access‚Üź'Shared'
              :Else ‚ćĚ Therefore, it MUST be "instanced"
                  access‚Üź'Instance'
               ‚ćĚ Only "instance" methods may be overridable:
                  :If ‚ą®/' overridable'‚ć∑buffer
                      more,‚Üź‚äā'Overridable'
                  :EndIf
              :EndIf
               ‚ćĚ Only "instance" methods may override:
              :If ‚ą®/' override'‚ć∑buffer
                  more,‚Üź‚äā'Override'
              :EndIf
          :ElseIf vs.isInterface
              type‚Üź'Method'
              access‚Üź'Instance'  ‚ćĚ Interface methods are always "Public" and therefore either "Instance" or "Shared"!
              buffer‚Üź''
          :Else
              :Return
          :EndIf
          keywords‚Üź({(1 ‚éēC 1‚ÜĎ‚ćĶ),‚éēC 1‚Üď‚ćĶ}¬®{' 'P.APLTreeUtils2.Split ‚ćĶ‚Üď‚ć®‚ćĶ‚ć≥' '}buffer)~'Public' 'Instance' 'Shared'
          :If (‚äā'private')‚ąä‚éēC keywords
              :Return
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
      remarks‚Üź''
      noOf‚Üź‚ČĘsource‚ÜźRemoveMultiLocalLines source
      :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘ{‚ćĶ/‚ć®'‚ćĚ'=‚ÜĎ¬®‚ćĶ}buffer‚Üź1‚ÜďnoOf‚ÜĎsource ‚ćĚ remarks
          buffer/‚ć®‚Üź{~‚ą®/‚ą®/¬®':access' ':implements'{‚ćļ‚Č°‚éēC(‚ČĘ‚ćļ)‚ÜĎ‚ćĶ}¬®‚äā‚ćĶ}‚ąėP.APLTreeUtils2.DLB¬®buffer
          buffer‚Üď¬®‚ć®‚Üź{+/‚ąß\' '=‚ćĶ}¬®buffer
          buffer‚ÜĎ‚ć®‚Üź+/‚ąß\'‚ćĚ'=‚ÜĎ¬®buffer
          buffer‚ĆŅ‚ć®‚Üź'‚ćĚ‚ćĚ'‚ąė‚ČĘ¬®2‚ÜĎ¬®buffer
      :AndIf 0‚Č†‚ČĘbuffer‚Üź1‚Üď¬®buffer
          buffer‚Üź(' '=‚ÜĎ¬®buffer)‚Üď¬®buffer
          remarks‚Üź{‚ćĶ,' '/‚ć®' '‚Č†‚ÜĎ¬Į1‚ÜĎ‚ćĶ}¬®buffer
      :EndIf
      :If IgnorePattern{0=‚ČĘ‚ćļ:1 ‚čĄ ‚ćļ‚ą®.‚Č†(‚ČĘ‚ćļ)‚ÜĎ‚ćĶ}name
           ‚ćĚ A method name may appear again: an included namespace may provide a
           ‚ćĚ method with a name also used in the container class. Therefore, any
