    ‚ąá r‚ÜźHandleVersionInHeader(ref header);txt;body;last;qdmx
    ‚ćĚ Handle special case: is there a function `Version`, and does it return the right stuff?
      r‚Üźheader
      :If ~ignoreVersion
          txt‚Üź''
          :If (‚äā'Version')‚ąäref.‚éēNL-3 ‚ćĚ Is there a "Version" function?
              :Trap 0 ‚ćĚ not nice, but these calls may fail for all sorts of reasons.
                  :If 9.1‚Č°‚éēNC‚äā‚ćēref  ‚ćĚ Is it an ordinary namespace?!
                      body‚Üźref.‚éēNR'Version'
                      txt‚Üź‚ćēref.{11::'' ‚čĄ ,‚ćé‚ćĶ}'Version'
                  :Else
                      txt‚Üź‚ćēref.Version
                  :EndIf
              :Else
                  qdmx‚Üź‚éēDMX
                  ‚éē‚Üź'Processing the "Version" function crashed (',qdmx.EM,')'
              :EndTrap
          :ElseIf (‚äā'Version')‚ąäref.‚éēNL-2 ‚ćĚ Is there a "Version" variable?
              txt‚Üź‚ćēref.Version
          :EndIf
          :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘtxt
              :If 2>|‚Č°txt
                  txt‚Üź‚äÜ{'+'‚ąä‚ćĶ:‚ćĶ‚ÜĎ‚ć®¬Į1+‚ćĶ‚ć≥'+' ‚čĄ ‚ćĶ}txt
              :Else
                  txt‚Üź{'Version ',({'+'‚ąä‚ćĶ:‚ćĶ‚ÜĎ‚ć®¬Į1+‚ćĶ‚ć≥'+' ‚čĄ ‚ćĶ}‚ćļ),' from ',‚ćĶ}/(3=‚ČĘtxt)‚Üďtxt
              :EndIf
              txt‚Üź('' '' '## Version'),txt
              :If 0=‚ČĘr
                  r‚Üź,‚äā'Txt'txt
              :Else
                  last‚Üź‚ČĘr
                  (last‚äÉr)‚Üźtxt{‚ćĶ[1],(‚äā(2‚äÉ‚ćĶ),‚ćļ)}last‚äÉr
              :EndIf
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá r‚ÜźHandleCopyRightInHeader(ref header);txt;body
    ‚ćĚ Handle special case: is there a function `Copyright`, and does it return the right stuff?
      r‚Üźheader
      :If ~_ignoreCopyright
          txt‚Üź''
          :If (‚äā'Copyright')‚ąäref.‚éēNL-3 ‚ćĚ Is there a "Copyright" function?
              txt‚Üź''
              :If 9.1‚Č°‚éēNC‚äā‚ćēref  ‚ćĚ Is it an ordinary namespace?!
                  body‚Üźref.‚éēNR'Copyright'
                  txt‚Üźref.{11::'' ‚čĄ ,‚ćé‚ćĶ}'Copyright'
              :Else
                  txt‚Üź{0 1‚ąä‚ć®‚Č°‚ćĶ:,‚äā‚ćĶ ‚čĄ 2=‚ćī‚ćī‚ćĶ:‚Üď‚ćĶ ‚čĄ ‚ćĶ},ref.Copyright
              :EndIf
          :ElseIf (‚äā'Copyright')‚ąäref.‚éēNL-2 ‚ćĚ Is there a "Copyright" variable?
              txt‚Üźref.Copyright
          :EndIf
          :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘtxt
              txt‚Üź('' '' '## Copyright'),,/txt
              :If 0=‚ČĘr
                  r‚Üź,‚äā'Txt'txt
              :Else
                  ((‚ČĘr)‚äÉr)‚Üźtxt{‚ćĶ[1],(‚äā(2‚äÉ‚ćĶ),‚ćļ)}(‚ČĘr)‚äÉr
              :EndIf
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
    ‚ąá
    ‚ąá r‚ÜźHandleHistoryInHeader(ref header);txt;body;last;source;buffer;bool
    ‚ćĚ Handle special case: is there a function `History`, and does it either return the right stuff
    ‚ćĚ or consist of comments useful for ADOC?
      r‚Üźheader
      :If ~_ignoreHistory
          txt‚Üź''
          :If (‚äā'History')‚ąäref.‚éēNL-3 ‚ćĚ Is there a "History" function?
              txt‚Üź''
              :If 0=‚ÜĎ‚ÜĎref.‚éēAT'History'
                  :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘtxt‚ÜźP.APLTreeUtils2.DLB 1‚Üďref.‚éēNR'History'
                  :AndIf 0‚Č†‚ČĘtxt‚Üź1‚Üď¬®('‚ćĚ'=‚ÜĎ¬®txt)/txt
                      txt‚Üź(‚Ćä/+/‚ąß\' '=‚äÉtxt)‚Üď¬®txt
                  :Else
                      source‚Üź‚éēSRC ref
                      buffer‚Üź'^\s*''.+''' '^\s*‚ćĚ.*$' '^\s*‚ąá\s*History\b'‚éēR(,¬®'&' '&' '‚ąá‚ąá')‚ć†('Greedy' 0)‚ä£source
                      :If 0<+/bool‚Üź‚ą®/¬®'‚ąá‚ąá'‚ąė‚ć∑¬®buffer
                          buffer‚Üź(bool‚ć≥1)‚Üďbuffer
                          buffer‚ÜźP.APLTreeUtils2.DLB(‚ÜĎ'^\s*‚ąá\s*$'‚éēS 2‚ć†('Greedy' 0)‚ä£buffer)‚ÜĎbuffer
                          :If 0=+/~(‚ÜĎ¬®buffer)‚ąä':‚ćĚ'
                              txt‚Üź1‚Üď¬®('‚ćĚ'=‚ÜĎ¬®buffer)/buffer
                          :EndIf
                      :EndIf
                  :EndIf
              :Else
                  :Trap 0 ‚ćĚ not nice, but these calls may very well fail
                      :If 9.1‚Č°‚éēNC‚äā‚ćēref  ‚ćĚ Is it an ordinary namespace?!
                          body‚Üźref.‚éēNR'History'
                          txt‚Üźref.{11::'' ‚čĄ ‚ćé‚ćĶ}'History'
                      :Else
                          txt‚Üźref.History
                      :EndIf
                  :EndTrap
              :EndIf
          :ElseIf (‚äā'History')‚ąäref.‚éēNL-2 ‚ćĚ Is there a "History" variable...
          :AndIf 0<‚ČĘref.History ‚ćĚ ... that is not empty?
              txt‚Üźref.History
          :EndIf
          :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘtxt
              :If 2=‚ćī‚ćītxt
                  txt‚Üź{'<pre>',‚ćĶ,'</pre>'}¬®‚Üď‚éēFMT txt
              :EndIf
              txt‚Üź{2=‚Č°‚ćĶ:‚ćĶ ‚čĄ ‚Üď‚ćĶ}txt
              txt‚Üź('' '' '## History'),txt
              :If 0=‚ČĘr
                  r‚Üź,‚äā'Txt'txt
              :Else
                  last‚Üź‚ČĘr
                  (last‚äÉr)‚Üźtxt{‚ćĶ[1],(‚äā(2‚äÉ‚ćĶ),‚ćļ)}last‚äÉr
              :EndIf
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
