    ‚ąá {r}‚Üź{embeddedClassNames}Analyze_ scriptRef;vs;buffer;bool;tmpFilename;source;A;name
      ‚ćĚ Analyzes a particular script and appends the result to the _META array.
      ‚ćĚ If the left argument is specified, only that (or these) embedded class(es) gets analyzed.
      ‚ćĚ Returns either an empty vector or a vector of character vectors with the name(s) of any embedded classes.
      A‚ÜźP.APLTreeUtils2
      r‚Üź‚ć¨
      vs‚Üź‚éēNS''
      vs.publishedStuff‚Üźvs.inheritsFrom‚Üź''
      vs.devisorMeta‚Üź‚ć¨
      vs.formattedScriptName‚Üź{‚ćĶ‚ÜĎ‚ć®1+-'.'‚ć≥‚ć®‚ĆĹ‚ćĶ}{‚ćĶ‚Üď‚ć®2√ó'#.'‚Č°2‚ÜĎ‚ćĶ}‚ćēscriptRef
      :Trap 16
          vs.origSource‚Üź{‚ćĶ‚Üď‚ć®+/‚ąß/' '=‚ćĶ}¬®‚éēSRC scriptRef
      :Else
          :If 9.1=‚éēNC‚äā‚ćēscriptRef
              #.‚éēSHADOW¬®'ADOC_Temp' 'ADOC_Source'
              'ADOC_Temp'#.‚éēNS''
              '#.ADOC_Source'scriptRef.‚éēNS‚ÜďscriptRef.‚éēNL 2 3 4
              #.ADOC_Source.‚éēEX #.ADOC_Source.‚éēNL 3.6 3.9 7.9   ‚ćĚ Delete external stuff, otherwise SALT will crash (Bug <01706>)
              scriptRef‚ÜźConvertOrdinaryNamespace2Scripted #.ADOC_Source
              vs.origSource‚Üź{‚ćĶ‚Üď‚ć®+/‚ąß/' '=‚ćĶ}¬®‚éēSRC scriptRef
              vs.origSource/‚ć®‚Üź1,~‚ąß\'‚ćĚ'=‚ÜĎ¬®1‚Üďvs.origSource    ‚ćĚ Get rid of any leading comments as they are not meaningful in this context
          :Else
              (‚ąÜEM‚Üź'Invalid right argument')‚éēSIGNAL 11
          :EndIf
