              r‚Üź{' 'P.APLTreeUtils2.Split P.APLTreeUtils2.DMB ‚ćĶ~'‚ąá'}r       ‚ćĚ split by blank, remove any dels first
              r‚Üź'‚ąá',2‚äÉr                     ‚ćĚ With operators it's always the second one
          :Else
