    ‚ąá {r}‚ÜźMergeWithDevisor devisor;currentMeta;name;this;scriptName;type;nameList;i;buffer
      ‚ćĚ Implicit argument: _META; is also modified
      currentMeta‚Üź(‚ČĘ_META)‚äÉ_META
      scriptName‚Üź1 1‚äÉdevisor
      type‚Üź1 2‚äÉdevisor
      r‚Üź''
      :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘbuffer‚Üź5‚äÉcurrentMeta
          nameList‚Üź'name'‚ąėGet 5‚äÉcurrentMeta
          :For i :In ‚ć≥‚ćī1 5‚äÉdevisor
              this‚Üźi‚äÉ1 5‚äÉdevisor
              name‚Üź'name'GetSingle this
              :If (‚äāname)‚ąänameList
                  this‚ÜźSet this'more'(‚äā'Inherited from "',scriptName,'" but re-defined')
                  (1 5 i‚äÉdevisor)‚Üźthis
              :Else
                  this‚ÜźSet this'more'(‚äā'Inherited from "',scriptName,'"')
                  (5‚äÉcurrentMeta)‚Üź(5‚äÉcurrentMeta),‚äāthis
              :EndIf
          :EndFor
          (5‚äÉcurrentMeta)‚ÜźAnalyzeResult 5‚äÉcurrentMeta
          ((‚ČĘ_META)‚äÉ_META)‚ÜźcurrentMeta
      :EndIf
