    ‚ąá vs‚ÜźInsertChapterToc vs;bool;First;this;no;Toc;i;anchor;buffer;level1Flag
     ‚ćĚ Inserts anchors to all "leading" <h{n}> tags and prepares a table-of-contents
     ‚ćĚ although this might be visible only if a certain number of entries is found.
     ‚ćĚ Adds to vs.Top
      :If _Toc
          Toc‚Üź‚äā'<div class="toctab">'
          :If 0<‚ČĘvs.Top
          :AndIf 0<+/bool‚Üź(‚ć≥‚ČĘvs.Top)‚ąä1+'<h[0-9]\b[^>]*>'‚éēS 0‚ć†('Mode' 'D')‚ä£vs.Top
              level1Flag‚Üź0‚Č†‚ČĘ'<h1\b[^>]*>'‚éēS 0‚ć†('Mode' 'D')‚ä£vs.Top
              vs.Top‚Üź(1,1‚Üďbool){‚éēML‚Üź0 ‚čĄ ‚ćļ‚äā‚ćĶ}vs.Top
              (First vs.Top)‚Üź{(1‚äÉ‚ćĶ)(1‚Üď‚ćĶ)}vs.Top
              :For i :In ‚ć≥‚ČĘvs.Top
                  this‚Üźi‚äÉvs.Top
                  no‚Üź‚ćéthis[3]
                  anchor‚Üź'toc_',GetChapterNo,':',¬Į4‚ÜĎ'0000',‚ćēi
                  this[this‚ć≥'>']‚Üź‚äā' id="',anchor,'">'
                  this‚Üź‚ąäthis
                  (i‚äÉvs.Top)‚Üźthis
                  buffer‚Üź'<div class="level',(‚ćē1‚Ćą6‚Ćäno),'">',nl
                  buffer,‚Üź'<a href="#',anchor,'">',({‚ćĶ‚ÜĎ‚ć®¬Į1+‚ćł'</h'‚ć∑‚ćĶ}{‚ćĶ‚Üď‚ć®‚ćĶ‚ć≥'>'}this),'</a>',nl,'</div>'
                  Toc,‚Üź‚äābuffer,nl
              :EndFor
              :If 0‚Č†‚ČĘvs.topLinks
                  Toc,‚Üź'<div class="level2"><a href="#',GetChapterNo,'_tocref">Reference</a></div>'
                  Toc,‚Üź{'<div class="level3">',‚ćĶ,'</div>'}¬®vs.topLinks[;2]
              :EndIf
              Toc‚Üź{0=‚ČĘ‚ćĶ:'' ‚čĄ ‚äÉ,/‚ćĶ}Toc
              vs.Top‚Üź(1‚äÉvs.Top),{0=‚ČĘ‚ćĶ:'' ‚čĄ ‚äÉ,/‚ćĶ}1‚Üďvs.Top
              :If level1Flag
                  vs.Top‚ÜźFirst,Toc,'</div>',vs.Top
              :Else
                  vs.Top‚Üź{‚ćĶ,Toc,'</div>',(‚ČĘ‚ćĶ)‚ÜďFirst,vs.Top}'<div class="header">'
              :EndIf
          :ElseIf 0‚Č†‚ČĘvs.topLinks
              Toc,‚Üź{'<div class="level2">',‚ćĶ,'</div>'}¬®vs.topLinks[;2]
              Toc,‚Üź'</div>'
              vs.Top,‚Üź'<div id="',GetChapterNo,'_toc">',(‚äÉ{0=‚ČĘ‚ćĶ:'' ‚čĄ ‚äÉ,/‚ćĶ}Toc),'</div>'
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
