    ‚ąá {append}WriteFile(filename data);fno;fullname;flag
    ‚ćĚ Write UTF-8 "data" to "filename".
    ‚ćĚ If the write operation fails it waits 0.2 seconds and then tries again. 
      :Access Public Shared
      append‚Üź{2=‚éēNC ‚ćĶ:‚ćé‚ćĶ ‚čĄ 0}'append'
      flag‚Üź0
      :Repeat
          :Trap 19 22
              fno‚Üźfilename ‚éēNTIE 0 17 ‚ćĚ Open exclusively
              filename ‚éēNERASE fno
              flag‚Üź1
          :CaseList 19
              ‚éēDL 0.2
          :Case 22
              flag‚Üź1 ‚ćĚ That's just fine
          :Else
              ‚éēDM ‚éēSIGNAL ‚éēEN
          :EndTrap
      :Until flag
      fno‚Üźfilename ‚éēNCREATE 0
      :If 160‚Č§‚éēDR data
          data‚Üź‚éēUCS'UTF-8'‚éēUCS data
      :EndIf
      data ‚éēNAPPEND fno
      ‚éēNUNTIE fno
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá {R}‚Üź{wait}Run cmd;‚ąÜWAIT;windowStyle;wsh
     ‚ćĚ Starts an application
     ‚ćĚ By default, Run doesn't wait for the app to quit.
