      windowStyle‚Üź8 ‚ćĚ is WINDOWSTYLE.NORMAL
      'wsh'‚éēWC'OLEClient' 'WScript.Shell'
      :Trap 0
          {}wsh.Run cmd windowStyle wait
      :Else
          R‚Üź1('.'‚éēWG'LastError')
      :EndTrap
